no_examples_td: There are no other specimens of this coin attributed to being minted during the reign of Tu Duc.

not_mm: This coin was not minted during the reign of Minh Mang.
not_td: This coin was not minted during the reign of Tu Duc.
not_tt: This coin was not minted during the reign of Thieu Tri.

meanings_hhttllll: Appreciate the wise, love one's parents, enjoy pleasure, benefit from gain
meanings_qtdapdvt: The state calm, the people at peace, the wind gentle, the rain beneficial
meanings_hptctbcn: The three desires of Hua, the Nine Comparisons in [the poem] Tianbao
meanings_dvdldddt: Achieve status, achieve riches, achieve reputation, achieve longevity
meanings_lpkttsdt: The Six Treasuries maintained perfectly, the Three Occupations performed correctly
meanings_ccccvdvt: Impartiality and rectitude at their utmost, impartiality without favouritism
meanings_vtvtvvtt: Ten thousand years, ten thousand years, ten thousand times ten thousand years, longevity
meanings_hltqncpd: When the rivers follow their course, the annual harvest is abundant
meanings_ttttllaa: Love one's parents, respect one's superiors, honour the old, cherish the children
meanings_qpbcnant: When the state is rich and the army is strong, there is peace at home, and calm abroad
meanings_nsnxncnp: Like a mountain, like a river, like a ridge, like a mound
meanings_qqttpptt: May the Prince be like a prince, the subject like a subject, the father like a father, the son like a son
meanings_pndhttns: Happiness [as vast] as the Eastern Sea, longevity [as old] as the Southern Mountains
meanings_vtdtvpdd: Ten thousand [years of] longevity as the [fitting] reward, ten thousand happinesses gather upon them
meanings_tbaddbab: Heaven does not care too much about its rules, Earth does not care too much about its treasures
meanings_ttkcknkt: His emblems are chiseled in metal and stone, they are made of gold and of jade
meanings_vdddtmdd: The Way of the King is vast, the teachings of the Wise man are immense
meanings_nnhkvtvc: The Unique Man [the King] is blessed by heaven, ten thousand [years] of longevity without limit
meanings_nttpttkn: Observe the propitious [movement] of the Five Planets, and all works will be achieved perfectly
meanings_thccvttc: The Four Seas pay homage, ten thousand generations transmit it
meanings_tthccvbl: With heavenly blessing, there is nothing that is not beneficial
meanings_nnhktdlc: The Unique Man [the King] is blessed by heaven, all the people turn to him
meanings_tcdtatvt: Act now, the time is right to benefit 10,000 generations
meanings_qgvnlcht: A state without fear, [such] benefit reaches later generations
meanings_cmptbhpd: As high and bright as the sky, as vast and deep as the earth
meanings_tlvtbhmc: With honours from heaven, he preserves the Mandate
meanings_hhldndnn: So brilliant is his virtue, good for the people, good for mankind
meanings_pvtdktvv: Moulded and enclosed by Heaven and Earth, taking meticulous care of all living things
meanings_uvtnttch: In all places and all times, [may you] receive the blessing of heaven
meanings_nknclvlv: Like the [jade] gui, like the [jade] zhang, let everyone know [of him], let everyone think [of him]
meanings_dlctdncs: Limit your mind with courtesy and decide things with justice
meanings_vvhnbtth: All things are good, hundreds of families are peaceful
meanings_nhlt: The primordial exerts his influence, propitious and virtuous
meanings_pltt: Happiness and success, peaceful and assured
meanings_ddqv: The virtue of the Emperor moves without limit
meanings_ldhs: Acquire the necessary goods, assure the well-being of the people
meanings_thvd: Balance and harmony, all in place, multiply
meanings_lptd: Achieve happiness and share it with the people
meanings_tpvt: To be a model throughout the empire
meanings_cktc: Firmness, strength, in the correct position, righteous
meanings_gcnt: The families are well provided for, the people have sufficient
meanings_tkvn: A longevity of ten thousand years
meanings_vvts: All living things are born from it
meanings_vtvl: Ten thousand generations will reap the results
meanings_dqld: Enrich the state, benefit the people
meanings_ctpc: Public and private affairs, rich and well provided for
meanings_pllt: Happiness and wealth will come aplenty
meanings_tddh: All the people have sincere affection for him
meanings_ccdt: The Nine Meritorious Acts must be carried out in order
meanings_klth: To weave (the immutable law) across the empire
meanings_tcdt: Rule according to the [Nine] Meritorious Acts, and imperial power will flourish
meanings_tcdh: All the affairs of State in harmony
